Class Human

  • java.lang.Object
    • greenfoot.Actor
      • Human
  • public abstract class Human
extends greenfoot.Actor
    Human class The people in the simulation, can be infected, died and recovred, and is divided into 3 different categoires by age, different categories have different shape being represented.
